# Seatech — Complete Project Documentation

> Everything built from start to finish. Every component, page, database table, service, and security measure.

---

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| **Framework** | React 18 + TypeScript (Vite) |
| **Routing** | React Router v6 |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS + Custom CSS variables (dark theme) |
| **Animations** | Framer Motion |
| **UI Components** | shadcn/ui (Radix UI primitives) |
| **Database** | Supabase (PostgreSQL) |
| **Auth** | Supabase Auth (email/password) |
| **Data Fetching** | TanStack React Query |
| **Form Handling** | React Hook Form + Zod validation |
| **Email (Inbound)** | Web3Forms API |
| **Email (Outbound)** | EmailJS |
| **SEO** | react-helmet-async |
| **Notifications** | Sonner (toast system) |
| **Deployment** | Vercel (CI/CD via GitHub) |
| **Version Control** | GitHub (`Seatech-Org/seatech`) |

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
seatech/
├── index.html              ← SEO meta tags, OG, Twitter Card, canonical URL
├── public/
│   ├── sitemap.xml         ← All pages listed for Google crawling
│   ├── robots.txt          ← Bot rules + sitemap reference
│   ├── logo.svg / logo2.svg / logo3.svg
│   └── categories/         ← Category images
├── src/
│   ├── App.tsx             ← Router + Providers + Lazy loading
│   ├── main.tsx            ← React entry point
│   ├── index.css           ← Design tokens, dark theme CSS variables
│   ├── pages/              ← 16 pages
│   ├── components/         ← 11 shared components + 16 shadcn UI components
│   ├── contexts/           ← CartContext
│   ├── services/           ← product-service.ts (Supabase + local fallback)
│   ├── utils/              ← email.ts (Web3Forms + EmailJS)
│   ├── data/               ← Local product catalog + client list
│   ├── integrations/       ← Supabase client + TypeScript types
│   ├── hooks/              ← Custom React hooks
│   └── assets/             ← Hero images, logo
├── supabase/
│   ├── migrations/         ← 8 SQL migration files
│   └── functions/          ← Edge functions
├── vercel.json             ← Vercel SPA routing config
└── .env                    ← Secrets (gitignored)
```

