## 🌐 Pages (16 Total)

### 1. [Index.tsx](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/src/pages/Index.tsx) — Homepage (`/`)
- Animated hero section with **cycling background images** (4 hero images, 5s interval)
- **Credibility card** (closeable badge showing trust indicators)
- **Trusted Partners** section — animated vertical scrolling logo carousel (all clients)
- **Ecosystem section** — 3 cards: Government Buying, Direct Buying, Strategic Selling
- **Why Seatech?** section — rotating testimonials synced to hero image timer
- **Call to Action** section with Get Started + Learn More buttons
- Floating **WhatsApp** button (with animated ping ring) + **Phone** button (fixed bottom-right)
- Full **JSON-LD structured data** (Organization + LocalBusiness + WebSite schemas)

### 2. [Products.tsx](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/src/pages/Products.tsx) — Product Catalog (`/products`)
- **3-level category navigation**: All → Furniture → Sub-categories → Products
- Category icons auto-assigned based on product name keywords
- **Sticky search bar** within the product view
- **URL-synced state**: category and search stored in query params (`?category=X&search=Y`)
- **Loading skeletons** while fetching
- **Empty state** with contextual messaging
- Responsive grid: 1→2→3→4 columns

### 3. [ProductDetailPage.tsx](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/src/pages/ProductDetailPage.tsx) — Product Detail (`/products/:productId`)
- Full product specs displayed in categorized table
- Image gallery with thumbnail selection
- Quantity selector with min order enforcement
- **Add to Quote** and **Add to Cart** buttons
- Seller badge with verified status
- Breadcrumb navigation back to category

### 4. [Admin.tsx](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/src/pages/Admin.tsx) — Admin Dashboard (`/admin`) 🔒 Admin only
- **4 tabs**: Quote Requests, Dealer Applications, OEM Requests, User Management
- **Quote management**: view all quotes, approve/reject with status dropdown
- **Status change** triggers EmailJS notification to customer
- **Dealer application** review with full business details
- **OEM authorization** request management
- **User role management**: promote/demote users between `admin` and `user`
- Uses `adminClient` (service role Supabase client) to bypass RLS for admin operations
- Real-time data via React Query with `refetchInterval`

### 5. [Dashboard.tsx](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/src/pages/Dashboard.tsx) — User Dashboard (`/dashboard`) 🔒 Auth required
- Shows logged-in user's **quote history**
- Quote status badges (pending / approved / rejected)
- Quote item breakdown
- **Dealer application status** tracker
- Profile information display
- Logout button

### 6. [Auth.tsx](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/src/pages/Auth.tsx) — Authentication (`/auth`)
- **Tabbed interface**: Sign In / Sign Up
- Email + password forms with Zod validation
- Sign up creates a Supabase user + inserts into `profiles` table
- Error handling with toast notifications
- Redirects to `/dashboard` on success

### 7. [Contact.tsx](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/src/pages/Contact.tsx) — Contact Page (`/contact`)
- **Contact info cards**: Email, Phone (toll-free), Corporate Office, Factory address
- **Inquiry form** (name, company, phone, email, requirements) 
