## 🗄️ Database Schema (Supabase / PostgreSQL)

### Tables (5)

#### `profiles`
Stores extended user info linked to Supabase Auth users.
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | UUID | FK → auth.users |
| company_name | TEXT | |
| contact_person | TEXT | |
| email | TEXT | |
| phone | TEXT | |
| address | TEXT | |
| gst_number | TEXT | |
| role | TEXT | `admin` or `user` |
| created_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | |

#### `dealer_applications`
Stores partner/dealer and OEM authorization requests.
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | UUID | Primary key |
| dealer_name | TEXT | |
| address | TEXT | |
| mobile | TEXT | |
| email | TEXT | |
| director_name | TEXT | |
| director_mobile | TEXT | |
| director_email | TEXT | |
| gst_number | TEXT | |
| turnover_year1/2/3 | NUMERIC | 3-year financials  |
| product_requirements | TEXT | |
| remarks | TEXT | |
| status | TEXT | `pending` / `approved` / `rejected` |
| created_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | |

#### `quotes`
Stores bulk quote requests submitted by users.
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | UUID | |
| user_id | UUID | FK → auth.users (nullable for guest) |
| status | TEXT | `pending` / `approved` / `rejected` |
| total_items | INT | |
| additional_remarks | TEXT | |
| created_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | |

#### `quote_items`
Individual line items within a quote.
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | UUID | |
| quote_id | UUID | FK → quotes |
| product_id | TEXT | |
| product_name | TEXT | |
| quantity | INT | |
| created_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | |

#### `user_roles`
Separate roles table (in addition to profile.role) for RLS policy checks.
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| id | UUID | |
| user_id | UUID | FK → auth.users |
| role | ENUM | `admin` or `user` |
| created_at | TIMESTAMPTZ | |

