## 📦 Product Service

[src/services/product-service.ts](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/src/services/product-service.ts) — dual-source strategy:
1. **Primary**: Fetches from Supabase `products` table (with inventory join + specs join)
2. **Fallback**: Uses local [src/data/products.ts](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/src/data/products.ts) if Supabase is empty or unreachable
3. Exposed as a **React Query hook** ([useProducts(filters)](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/src/services/product-service.ts#88-95)) — automatically caches, revalidates, handles loading states

