## 🔍 SEO Implementation

### [index.html](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/index.html) (Static meta tags)
- Full `<title>` with brand + keywords
- `<meta name="description">` — keyword-rich 160-char description
- `<meta name="keywords">` — 10+ targeted terms including "Seatech"
- `<meta name="robots">` — `index, follow, max-image-preview:large`
- Canonical URL
- Open Graph (og:title, og:description, og:image, og:type, og:locale)
- Twitter Card (summary_large_image)
- Geo tags (`geo.region: IN`, `geo.country: India`)
- Preconnect hints for Google Fonts

### [SEO.tsx](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/src/components/SEO.tsx) (Dynamic per-page meta via react-helmet-async)
Used on every page — overrides [index.html](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/index.html) tags with page-specific content:
- Prevents duplicate "| Seatech" if title already contains brand name
- Injects JSON-LD structured data on homepage

### JSON-LD Structured Data (Homepage)
Three schema.org types injected:
- **Organization** — name, logo, contact, services, founded date
- **LocalBusiness** — address, hours, offer catalog with 5 services
- **WebSite** — URL, name, publisher link

### [public/sitemap.xml](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/public/sitemap.xml)
Lists all 10 public pages with:
- `<loc>` (full URL)
- `<lastmod>` (date)
- `<changefreq>` (weekly/monthly/yearly)
- `<priority>` (1.0 for homepage, down to 0.6 for minor pages)

### [public/robots.txt](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/public/robots.txt)
- Allows all bots to crawl public pages
- Blocks `/admin`, `/dashboard`, `/auth`, `/cart`
- Points to [sitemap.xml](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/public/sitemap.xml)

