## 🚀 Deployment

### Vercel
- Connected to `github.com/Seatech-Org/seatech`
- **Auto-deploys** on every `git push` to `main`
- Domain: `seatech-gov.com`
- [vercel.json](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/vercel.json) configured for SPA routing (all routes → [index.html](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/index.html))

### Environment Variables (in Vercel + local [.env](file:///Users/huzaifa/DevZoro/seatech/.env))
| Variable | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `VITE_SUPABASE_URL` | Supabase project URL |
| `VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY` | Anon (public) Supabase key |
| `VITE_SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` | Admin Supabase key (server-side only) |
| `VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY` | Web3Forms API key for inbound emails |
| `VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID` | EmailJS service ID |
| `VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID` | EmailJS template ID |
| `VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY` | EmailJS public key |

