## ⚡ Performance Optimizations

| Optimization | How |
|---|---|
| **Code splitting** | All 16 pages are lazy-loaded with `React.lazy()` |
| **Loading fallback** | Animated logo spinner shown while page chunks load |
| **React Query caching** | Product data cached and shared across components |
| **Image optimization** | `OptimizedImage` component with lazy loading |
| **Preconnect hints** | `<link rel="preconnect">` for Google Fonts in `index.html` |
| **Scroll restoration** | `ScrollToTop` component resets position on navigation |

---

## 🎨 Design System

- **Dark theme** by default — CSS custom properties (`--background`, `--foreground`, `--primary`, etc.)
- **Primary color**: Blue (`hsl(217, 91%, 60%)`)
- **Border radius**: Rounded corners throughout (`rounded-[10px]`, `rounded-full`)
- **Glass effects**: `backdrop-blur` + `border-white/[0.08]` borders for subtle depth
- **Animations**: Framer Motion for page transitions, hover states, entrance animations
- **Typography**: System sans-serif with tight tracking on headings

